{"tid":2157494,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"千萬不要再玩 282 大奇蹟日令中共春袋感到陰陰痛","createTime":"2020-08-15T05:28:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T06:54:55.000Z","uid":261388,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b74a95fb207a86b362929eace14ef4195504da9e","tid":2157494,"uid":261388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T05:28:17.000Z","msg":"出面好多風向POST 黑化 282 大奇蹟日 ，因為係中共心入面，香港人死撚哂都無問題，最重要就係香港個賭場正常運作，所以中共既策略係收緊香港社會自由，但係保持賭場落注自由，等佢可以吸美金續命<br />\n<br />\n點解話282大奇蹟日令到中共感到春袋陰陰痛，因為中共係賭場打壓香港人表態，就要拍打自己春袋，我當下次佢又見到282 暴升，停282 牌，會直接損害左賭場既自由性，萬惡既美帝又會玩野， 停完282牌之後，又可以721 831 果日炒721 831，佢又一步收緊可能要呢D 股改代號，當日停牌，但係香港人又可以諗其他方法表態，中共唔理又好撚無面 ，以小學生性格一定忍唔撚住拍打自己春袋，最後結果就係打爆自己春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最後香港連買股票都犯黨安法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />叫人買股票又犯黨安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  所有上市公司都要簽同意書效忠共產黨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以大家千萬唔好抄黃股 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b33135a3e7054abd51b4fe4e410172c92a4a1d4","tid":2157494,"uid":261388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T06:46:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c12d9c92e35bfa84fa877da973890d07f8b9da4f","tid":2157494,"uid":261388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T06:53:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a1a67f3291a3e682f5c6a9f2361ebb87e3cb115","tid":2157494,"uid":261388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T06:54:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}